==Description==

The [[Image:Sketcher_CreateRectangle_Center.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreateRectangle_Center|Sketcher CreateRectangle Center]] tool creates a centered rectangle. {{Version|1.0}}: This is the same tool as [[Sketcher_CreateRectangle|Sketcher CreateRectangle]] but with a different initial mode.

[[Image:SketcherCreateCenteredRectangleExample.png‎]]

==Usage==

See also: [[Sketcher_Workbench#Drawing_aids|Drawing aids]].

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_CreateRectangle_Center.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_CreateRectangle_Center|Centered rectangle]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketcher → Sketcher geometries → [[Image:Sketcher_CreateRectangle_Center.svg|16px]] Create centered rectangle}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|G}} then {{KEY|V}}.
# For further steps see [[Sketcher CreateRectangle#Usage|Sketcher CreateRectangle]].


